Name: Dinosaur Bundle Amigurumi Crochet Kit
Long desc:
Start your own Jurassic Park with this dinosaur crochet kit! This kit includes all the materials you need to make up to 8 dinosaurs, including a T-rex, Stegosaurus, Triceratops, and Brontosaurus! It even includes instructions for how to customize your dinos with pattern variations and all the colors are interchangeable, meaning you can choose your dinos colors!
Finished dinosaurs measure from 2″ – 4″ tall (depending on the dino).
Kit includes the pattern bundle with 4 unique dinosaur patterns, each with their own full-length video tutorials so you never miss a stitch! Plus a 1 month membership giving you access to hundreds of alternative patterns, including an additional 4 dinos!
*Crocheting 101: How to Crochet for Complete Beginners Included!*
Short desc:
Description
Kit includes:
• 100% Cotton Amigurumi Yarn
– Yellow
– Blue
– Purple
– Pink
– White
• Plastic Safety Bead Eyes x 16
• Pipe Cleaners x 2
• Stuffing
• Darning Needle
• Ergonomic Crochet Hook (Size G6/4.00mm)
• Foldable Scissors!
polish_Name: Zestaw do szydełkowania Amigurumi z dinozaurami
polish_Long desc:
Rozpocznij własny Park Jurajski z tym zestawem do szydełkowania dinozaurów! Ten zestaw zawiera wszystkie materiały potrzebne do zrobienia do 8 dinozaurów, w tym T-rexa, Stegozaura, Triceratopsa i Brontozaura! Zawiera nawet instrukcje, jak dostosować dinozaury za pomocą różnych wzorów, a wszystkie kolory są wymienne, co oznacza, że ​​możesz wybrać kolory dinozaurów!
Ukończone dinozaury mają od 2″ do 4″ wysokości (w zależności od dinozaura).
Zestaw zawiera pakiet wzorów z 4 unikalnymi wzorami dinozaurów, każdy z własnymi pełnometrażowymi samouczkami wideo, dzięki czemu nigdy nie przegapisz żadnego oczka! Plus 1-miesięczne członkostwo zapewniające dostęp do setek alternatywnych wzorów, w tym dodatkowych 4 dinozaurów!

Name: Crocheting 101 – Starter Kit
Long desc:
Yarning for a new hobby? Crocheting 101 will teach you not only how to crochet, but also how to make 6 unique projects along the way to not only help practice, but put your new skills to the test! Crocheting 101 is built to accommodate any learning style with 25 unique videos and a full 200 page eBook teaching you how to crochet stitch by stitch.
Kit includes all the yarn, hooks, stitch markers and needles I use throughout the series; everything needed to practice crocheting, make the 6 unique projects, and even have a bit left over to eat in case of emergency!

Description

Name: Seasonal Kit — Space Crafts
Long desc:
In this seasonal kit inspired by the cosmos, you'll find a variety of space-themed projects, from aliens and UFOs, to the stars in the sky, and even the planet Earth! With a string of lights and keychain, stuffing, eyes, and thread, plus our exclusive Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton yarn, this crochet kit has everything you need to never miss a stitch on these interstellar creations.

This kit includes all the materials you'll need to make all 6 projects in the themed season PLUS 3 month's of Club Crochet Pattern Membership with access to over 300 additional patterns in the library!

Name: Bonsai Tree and Pot Crochet Kit
Long desc:
I kept killing my bonsai tree’s, but with this how-to crochet kit you can crocheting one that you’ll never need to water! The pattern is relatively easy but leaves a lot for customization. Your final tree will measure about 5″ tall and you’ll be able to crochet a pot for it to go in, or learn to make your bonsai fit any pots you want! The instructions include a full unique video tutorial to help you get through the tough parts!
This pattern is achievable for BEGINNERS. Visit Crocheting101.com for a free series for complete beginners.
*Includes full-length video tutorial for the more difficult parts of the pattern!*

• Left handed video version available

– Brown

• Stuffing

polish_Long desc:
Ciągle zabijałam swoje drzewka bonsai, ale z tym zestawem do szydełkowania możesz zrobić takie, którego nigdy nie będziesz musiał podlewać! Wzór jest stosunkowo łatwy, ale pozostawia wiele do personalizacji. Twoje ostateczne drzewko będzie miało około 5 cali wysokości i będziesz mógł zrobić na szydełku doniczkę, w której będzie rosło, lub nauczyć się, jak sprawić, by Twoje bonsai pasowało do dowolnych doniczek! Instrukcje zawierają kompletny, unikalny samouczek wideo, który pomoże Ci przejść przez trudne części!
Ten wzór jest możliwy do wykonania dla POCZĄTKUJĄCYCH. Odwiedź Crocheting101.com, aby uzyskać bezpłatną serię dla kompletnych nowicjuszy.

Short desc:
Description
Materials:
• The Yarn (Worsted Weight)
– Green (Skin Tone)
– Black (Clothes / Hair)
– Purple (Shirt / Hat Detail)
– Yellow (Hat Detail)
– Brown (Broom)
• Size G6/4.00mm Hook
• Plastic Saftey Bead Eyes
• Stuffing
• NeedleGauge: 5 Rnds and 4 sts per 1” | Finished piece is about 2” tallWorked in the Round The Stitches:
– Ch : Chain stitch
– St : Stitch
– Sl.st : Slip Stitch
– Sc : Single Crochet
– Hdc : Half-Double Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase
– InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– FLO : Front Loops Only
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook

Short desc:
Description
Materials:

– Color A (Main color)
– Color B (Hooves/Nose)
– Fuzzy Color (Mane/Tail)
• Size G6/4.00mm Hook
• Plastic Saftey Bead Eyes
• Stuffing
• Needle
Gauge: 5 Rnds and 4 sts per 1” | Finished piece is about 2” tall
Worked in the Round
The Stitches:
– Ch : Chain stitch
– St : Stitch
– Sl.st : Slip Stitch
– Sc : Single Crochet
– Hdc : Half-Double Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase – InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook
For color changes in Bobble Stitches: [Blue/Red/Green] = [Step 3/Step 1/Step 2]

– Łańcuszek: Oczko

1. Narzuć włóczkę, włóż szydełko w oczko

– Sc : Single Crochet
– Hdc : Half-Double Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase – InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook
For color changes in Bobble Stitches: [Blue/Red/Green] = [Step 3/Step 1/Step 2]

Short desc:
Description
Materials:
• The Yarn (Worsted Weight)
– Purple (Clothing)
– Gold (Crown / Shoulder pads)
– Blue (Dress Detail / Jem)
– White (Undershirt / Dress)
– Sand (Skin Tone)
– Yellow (Hair)
* Black Thread (Eyeliner)
• Size G6/4.00mm Hook
• Plastic Saftey Bead Eyes
• Stuffing
• NeedleGauge: 5 Rnds and 4 sts per 1” | Finished piece is about 2” tallWorked in the Round The Stitches:
– Ch : Chain stitch
– St : Stitch
– Sl.st : Slip Stitch
– Sc : Single Crochet
– Hdc : Half-Double Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase
– InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook

Short desc:
Description
Materials:
• The Yarn (Worsted Weight)
• Size G6/4.00mm Hook
• Plastic Saftey Bead Eyes
• Stuffing
• NeedleGauge: 5 Rnds and 4 sts per 1” | Finished piece is about 2” tallWorked in the Round The Stitches:

– St : Stitch

1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch

4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total

– Light Purple (Main color)
– Gold (Armor / Gauntlet)
– Navy (Undershirt)
– Grey (Armor)

– Black (Shoes)

Gauge: 5 Rnds and 4 sts per 1” | Finished piece is about 3″ tall

The Stitches:
– Ch : Chain stitch
– St : Stitch
– Sl.st : Slip Stitch
– Sc : Single Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase
– InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook
For color changes in Bobble Stitches: [Blue/Red/Green] = [Step 3/Step 1/Step 2]

The Stitches:
– Ch : Chain stitch
– St : Stitch
– Sl.st : Slip Stitch
– Sc : Single Crochet
– Hdc : Half-Double Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase
– InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook

The Stitches:
– Ch : Chain stitch
– St : Stitch
– Sl.st : Slip Stitch
– Sc : Single Crochet
– Hdc : Half-Double Crochet
– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase
– InvDec : Invisible Decrease
– BLO : Back Loops Only
– Bo : Bobble Stitch
1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch
2. Yarn over and pull through
3. Yarn over and pull through 2 loops
4. Repeat steps 1 – 3 four times total
5. Yarn over and pull through all the loops on the hook
For color changes in Bobble Stitches: [Blue/Red/Green] = [Step 3/Step 1/Step 2]

Long desc:
*Patterns can be downloaded and accessed immediately after purchase*
In this crochet pattern bundle we’ll be crocheting a variety of miniature whale amigurumi! This pattern bundle is designed for complete beginners to advanced crocheters and will help you not only learn to crochet, but advance your skill with new and exciting techniques!
Every pattern in this bundle includes a full length video tutorial alongside an interactive PDF with checkmarks and time codes to keep track of your progress.
Pattern Bundle Includes:
• Beginner Whale Amigurumi – Learn how to crochet!
• Dolphin Amigurumi
• Narwhal Amigurumi
• Orca Amigurumi
• Beluga Amigurumi
• Mini Whales

– Dec/Inc : Decrease/Increase
– InvDec : Invisible Decrease

1. Yarn over, insert hook into stitch

Long desc:
Stitch together your own collection of amigurumi with this ultimate crochet kit bundle! This build your own bundle includes 4 different crochet kits each making up to 10 different amigurumi projects for 30+ different crochet creations! Crochet a series of Dinosaurs, Whales, Strawberries, Bonsai Trees, Suns and Cacti with this bundle of crochet kits at discount!

• Whale Crochet Kit

Plus a 4 month membership giving you access to hundreds of alternative patterns, including a whole library of additional projects!

polish_Long desc:
Zszyj własną kolekcję amigurumi z tym najlepszym zestawem do szydełkowania! Ten zestaw do samodzielnego zbudowania zawiera 4 różne zestawy do szydełkowania, z których każdy pozwala na wykonanie do 10 różnych projektów amigurumi na ponad 30 różnych szydełkowych kreacji! Zrób na szydełku serię dinozaurów, wielorybów, truskawek, drzewek bonsai, słońc i kaktusów z tym zestawem zestawów do szydełkowania ze zniżką!

• Zestaw do szydełkowania dinozaurów

• Zestaw do szydełkowania truskawek
• Zestaw do szydełkowania bonsai

Name: Yarn Darning Needle Bottle – Pack of 4
Long desc: This pack of darning needles includes 4 large eye aluminum needles in a rainbow of colors. Each needle features a bent end making them perfect for going in and out of hard to reach stitches. All 4 needles are neatly packaged in a re-useable bottle, making it easy to store!
Short desc:
Description
High Quality – These needles with large eye are made of durable aluminum, with a smooth finish, leaving no problems with snagging yarn.
Easy to Use – Due to the extra large eye, these needles are easy to thread yarn through even without a threader. The bent tip tapestry needle is easier to hook under stitches, and they are durable and lightweight.
Easy to Store – Our yarn needles with large eye include a clear bottle for storage. When you finish your project, just put our yarn needles into the bottle and don’t need to worry about losing your finishing needles!
Easy to Find – The 4 needles included come in a rainbow of different colors, making them easy to find and great for contrasting colors with projects!

Łatwe w użyciu – Dzięki wyjątkowo dużemu oczku, te igły są łatwe do nawlekania włóczki nawet bez nawlekacza. Zagięta końcówka igły gobelinowej jest łatwiejsza do zaczepienia pod ściegiem, a także jest trwała i lekka.

Name: Nature Color Pack – Amigurumi Cotton Yarn 4 Ball Bundle
Long desc:
Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton yarn is a natural, high quality, 100% cotton yarn. Specially designed for amigurumi, this 4-ply worsted weight yarn consists of multi-ply fibers which makes our yarn stronger and more vibrant, as well as giving excellent stitch definition and a split-proof nature.
Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton Yarn is great for beginners, as it’s more densely packed fibers provide a slightly chunkier nature making it easy to crochet with, provides more consistent stitch gauge, and make your stitches easy to distinguish! This color pack includes four (4) balls of yarn in nature themed colors (Sage Green, Forest Green, Pastel Yellow, and Nature Brown). Conveniently machine washable and dry-able for easy care.
Short desc:
Description
Content: 100% Cotton
Ball Size (Each): 63g / 2.2oz, 200ft / 61m / 67yd
Colors (4): Sage Green, Forest Green, Pastel Yellow, and Nature Brown
Care: Machine wash and dry
Gauge: 4 Medium Worsted
Recommended Crochet Hook: 4 mm (US G-6) – 5 mm (US H-8)
polish_Name: Nature Color Pack – Amigurumi Cotton Yarn 4 Ball Bundle
polish_Long desc:
Przędza Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton to naturalna, wysokiej jakości, w 100% bawełniana przędza. Specjalnie zaprojektowana do amigurumi, ta 4-warstwowa przędza worsted weight składa się z włókien wielowarstwowych, co sprawia, że ​​nasza przędza jest mocniejsza i bardziej żywa, a także zapewnia doskonałą definicję ściegu i jest odporna na rozdwajanie.
Przędza Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton jest świetna dla początkujących, ponieważ jej gęściej upakowane włókna zapewniają nieco grubszą naturę, co ułatwia szydełkowanie, zapewnia bardziej spójny wskaźnik ściegu i sprawia, że ​​ściegi są łatwe do rozróżnienia! Ten zestaw kolorów zawiera cztery (4) kulki włóczki w kolorach o tematyce natury (szałwiowa zieleń, leśna zieleń, pastelowa żółć i naturalny brąz). Wygodnie nadaje się do prania w pralce i suszenia w celu łatwej pielęgnacji.
polish_Short desc:

Name: Vaporwave Color Pack – Amigurumi Cotton Yarn 4 Ball Bundle
Long desc:
Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton yarn is a natural, high quality, 100% cotton yarn. Specially designed for amigurumi, this 4-ply worsted weight yarn consists of multi-ply fibers which makes our yarn stronger and more vibrant, as well as giving excellent stitch definition and a split-proof nature.
Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton Yarn is great for beginners, as it’s more densely packed fibers provide a slightly chunkier nature making it easy to crochet with, provides more consistent stitch gauge, and make your stitches easy to distinguish! This color pack includes four (4) balls of yarn in retro-vaporwave themed colors (Purple, Pink, Cyan, and Teal). Conveniently machine washable and dry-able for easy care.
Short desc:
Description
Content: 100% Cotton
Ball Size (Each): 63g / 2.2oz, 200ft / 61m / 67yd
Colors (4): Purple, Cyan, Pink, and Teal
Care: Machine wash and dry
Gauge: 4 Medium Worsted
Recommended Crochet Hook: 4 mm (US G-6) – 5 mm (US H-8)
polish_Name: Vaporwave Color Pack – Amigurumi Cotton Yarn 4 Ball Bundle
polish_Long desc:
Przędza Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton to naturalna, wysokiej jakości, w 100% bawełniana przędza. Specjalnie zaprojektowana do amigurumi, ta 4-warstwowa przędza worsted weight składa się z włókien wielowarstwowych, co sprawia, że ​​nasza przędza jest mocniejsza i bardziej żywa, a także zapewnia doskonałą definicję ściegu i jest odporna na rozdwajanie.
Przędza Club Crochet Amigurumi Cotton jest świetna dla początkujących, ponieważ jej gęściej upakowane włókna zapewniają nieco grubszą naturę, co ułatwia szydełkowanie, zapewnia bardziej spójny wskaźnik ściegu i sprawia, że ​​ściegi są łatwe do rozróżnienia! Ten zestaw kolorów zawiera cztery (4) kulki włóczki w kolorach o tematyce retro-vaporwave (fioletowy, różowy, cyjan i turkusowy). Wygodnie nadaje się do prania w pralce i suszenia w celu łatwej pielęgnacji.
